data.description: Your new home has been lovingly maintained and freshly painted inside, roof was replaced in 2022, gutters and gutter guards added, kitchen updated in 2021 with custom live edge bar tops, tile backsplash, LVP floors.  Master bath shower recently upgraded and a large soaking tub.  Two other bedrooms, full bath as well as bonus room are upstairs. Outside features a large lot, deck, hardie siding on home and invisible fence.  Your new neighborhood has a pond and is centrally located to both downtown Fuquay Varina and Holly Springs.
